title: Listen to Lady Gaga's voice without music during her Super Bowl 51 performance
text:
Updated at 8:40 a.m. ET 
Updated at 8:40 a.m. ET 
Lady Gaga's Super Bowl 51 halftime show was impressive, but this video may give you a newfound appreciation for her talent. 
Thanks to the power of technology, YouTuber Arkadiusz Tuszek was able to isolate Lady Gaga's vocals from the performance. 
The results are stunning.
